For everyone else who r getting it low.

1. Download latest k-lite codec pack.
2. Run the movie
3. Go to AC3 configuration "Mixer", uncheck "Auto gain control" and "Auto Matrix". Now change the "Column C" value to 5 in the "Mixing Matrix".
4. Press OK
